FBIS3-16282 "drsov050_b_94014" FBIS-SOV-94-050 Document Type:Daily Report 12 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Economic Issues Stavropol in Barter Deals With Bashkirs, Azerbaijan PM1503085994 Moscow SELSKAYA ZHIZN in Russian 12 Mar 94 p 1 PM1503085994 Moscow SELSKAYA ZHIZN Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report under "How We Will Enter the Field" rubric: "Fuel in Exchange for Grain"] [Text] Stavropol -- In exchange for 200,000 tonnes of grain, Stavropol Kray inhabitants will receive from Bashkortostan diesel fuel, gasoline, and the oils necessary for spring sowing. This decision was adopted during a working trip to Stavropol Kray by Aleksandr Rykov, Bashkortostan minister of material resources and interregional ties. The people of Stavropol Kray have also concluded an accord on an exchange of grain for petroleum products with Azerbaijan's oil refiners.
